    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2009-03-03</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-03-13T20:52:36Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Damaged Vehicle Information Act - Directs the Secretary of Transportation to issue a regulation to require persons who terminate a motor vehicle contract due to flood or water damage, collision, fire damage, theft and recovery, or any circumstance that adversely affects the fair market value of the vehicle to disclose information of such vehicle damage to the public.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Damaged Vehicle Information Act</title>
